# --- Protect private / sensitive material from being pushed ---
# Best protection is simply NOT copying these files into this folder.
# The patterns below are a safety net. They are intentionally SPECIFIC so they
# don't catch legitimate words like "example", "upgrade", or "finalize".

# Student records (FERPA) — folders
Grade/
Grades/

# Copyrighted textbook
Textbook/
Introduction-to-Mechatronics*.pdf

# Exam / quiz / solution materials (word-boundary patterns, not bare substrings)
*answer-key*
*answer_key*
*[Ss]olution[s]?.*
*-[Ss]olution*
*_[Ss]olution*
ME435_*Exam*
*Midterm*
*Final-Exam*
*[Qq]uiz-*

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
__MACOSX/
Thumbs.db
*.asv
